    <item>
      <title>里夫斯的英国愿景因市场衰退面临新的危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/reeves-vision-for-britain-faces-fresh-peril-from-market-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯将于周二在英国遭遇市场动荡以来首次在议会发表讲话，这是本周工党领导层面临的几个潜在爆发点之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/reeves-vision-for-britain-faces-fresh-peril-from-market-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛的斯尼德表示正等待中国推出刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/goldman-s-sneader-says-in-waiting-mode-for-china-stimulus-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团亚太区（日本除外）总裁凯文·斯尼德 (Kevin Sneader) 表示，在去年下半年看到一些发展势头之后，高盛集团和客户正在观望中国政府是否会推出重大刺激措施来重振经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/goldman-s-sneader-says-in-waiting-mode-for-china-stimulus-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:55:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国进口创纪录推动铁矿石需求上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/iron-ore-advances-after-record-china-imports-boost-demand-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示，中国年度炼钢原料进口量达到创纪录水平，且贸易顺差大幅增加，此后铁矿石价格再次飙升至每吨 100 美元以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/iron-ore-advances-after-record-china-imports-boost-demand-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:53:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税报告导致美元走弱，铜价延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/copper-extends-rally-as-dollar-weakens-on-trump-tariff-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称，即将上任的特朗普政府将缓慢提高贸易关税，而不是一次性征收巨额关税，铜价延续了今年的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/copper-extends-rally-as-dollar-weakens-on-trump-tariff-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:27:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台币将取代人民币成为亚洲主要融资货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/taiwan-dollar-set-to-replace-yuan-as-asia-s-top-funding-currency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利率和汇率波动风险较低，台币即将取代人民币成为亚洲最佳套利交易目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/taiwan-dollar-set-to-replace-yuan-as-asia-s-top-funding-currency</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:22:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
