    <item>
      <title>全球供应风险加剧，油价持于五个月高位附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯实施更严厉的制裁，以及即将上任的特朗普政府可能实施的贸易关税，对全球供应构成威胁，油价维持在五个月高位附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-14</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 23:27:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：关税报告推动美元下跌，中国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有消息称，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的经济团队成员讨论了逐步提高关税的方法，中国股市引领亚洲股市走高，而美元则走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 22:37:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
